videos.description: Kenisha Bell finds a wide open Irene Garrido who knocks down a 3-pointer to beat the halftime buzzer and give Minnesota a 27-26 lead over Nebraska.
videos.headline: Minnesota's Garrido nails halftime buzzer-beating 3-pointer
